io.vertx.ext.shell

Interface ShellServer


  • public interface ShellServer
    The shell server.

    A shell server is associated with a collection of term servers: the registerTermServer(TermServer) method registers a term server. Term servers life cycle are managed by this server.

    When a term server receives an incoming connection, a JobController instance is created and associated with this connection.

    The createShell() method can be used to create JobController instance for testing purposes.

    Author:
    Julien Viet
